profile:
We pride ourselves on our commitment to providing the highest quality of work, accompanied by contractors who are reliable, honest, and professional.
At CapaReno, we understand that where you live is not just your house – it’s your home, and that’s why we put our best construction boot forward to make sure your vision for your home renovation comes to life. Our skilled contractors will not only listen to what you hope to achieve, but will also provide guidance that is backed by expertise and compliance to current safety standards and building codes.
 
Regardless of the size of your project, we’ll take it seriously, approaching each task as if we were completing it in our own home. (Heck, we may even start to refer to it as our ‘home away from home’…)
 
At CapaReno, we value communication, and strive to build a professional relationship with our customers that is honest and respectful, while ensuring we remain approachable throughout the entire project. We will show up when we say we will, we will be transparent in our approach, and we will finish the jobs we start, with an end goal of not only meeting but exceeding your expectations.

Find out more about us online at www.caparenovations.com or check us out on Facebook by searching 'CapaReno Inc.'.
